    <title metal:fill-slot="title">The DOAP Network: Project and Product
    Registration in Launchpad
    </title>

<body>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

    <h1>Welcome to DOAP!</h1>

    <p>This is the Description of a Project web service, where we catalogue
    all the open source projects registered in The Launchpad. You can read
    more about the "Description Of A Project" framework
    <a href="+about">here</a>. We urge you to register your open source
    project with The Launchpad.</p>

	<ul>

        <li><a href="projects/">Find Project</a>: find your open source
        project if it has been registered in The Launchpad.</li>

		<li><a href="projects/+search">Advanced Project Search</a>: 
        Search for projects that are not only registered in the Launchpad
        but which are also available for translating, or have bugs listed,
        or have their source code available as Bazaar branches.</li>

        <li><a href="projects/+new">Register Project</a>: register an open
        source project with The Launchpad.</li>

        <li><a href="products/">Find Product</a>: find your open source
        product if it has been registered in The Launchpad.</li>

		<li><a href="products/+search">Advanced Product Search</a>: 
        Search for products that are not only registered in the Launchpad
        but which are also available for translating, or have bugs listed,
        or have their source code available as Bazaar branches.</li>

        <li><a href="products/+new">Register Product</a>: register an open
        source product with The Launchpad.</li>

	</ul>

</div>
</body>
</html>

